RiseIT Consulting is the first student-led IT consulting sandbox that bridges the gap between classroom learning and real industry practice â€” empowering the next generation of IT leaders and consultants.

We aim to equip tech-driven students with the consulting mindset, problem-solving skills, and professional exposure they need to make an impact in Indonesia's digital future.

